irc-chatter (0.3.1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Upgraded libcommuni to 1.2
  * Bug fix - command parse errors appear correctly
  * Bug fix - nick name changes are handled correctly
  * Bug fix - channel user list remains consistent
  * Readded the no predictive and no auto uppercase hints from the chat text (now it works)

 -- Timur Kristóf <venemo@msn.com>  Sun, 04 Nov 2012 02:12:22 +0200

irc-chatter (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=low

  * Facelift for start page
  * New start page appearance when no servers are set up
  * Facelift for manage servers page
  * Removed the old "Connecting, please wait" dialog
  * Automatic reconnection on socket errors
  * Added time stamp to join/part/leave messages and nick changes
  * Added userlist name count to UI
  * Removed the no predictive and no auto uppercase hints from the chat text
  * Added support for channel keys
  * Upgraded libcommuni to 1.1
  * Bug fix - automatic reconnection after disconnection
  * Bug fix - HTML no longer appears in notifications
  * Bug fix - Close button no longer appears for the server
  * Bug fix - Channel names are now handled in a case-insensitive way
  * Bug fix - Delete button will not appear for servers which are not added

 -- Timur Kristóf <venemo@msn.com>  Sun, 04 Nov 2012 00:41:22 +0200

