  * Improved server setting list interface
  * Added connection indicator to the server management page
  * "Connecting, please wait" will appear for a shorter time
  * Fixed a bug when random text was entered into the text field
  * Fixed a bug with connectivity
  * Fixed a bug after reconnecting to a server
  * Fixed a bug with notifications
  * The main text area will always scroll down

