irc-chatter (0.2.90) unreleased; urgency=low

  * Added support for connecting to multiple servers
  * Improved handling of offline state
  * Offline state is now displayed to the user
  * New settings, more customization
  * Notifications now work
  * Channel join UI is easier to use
  * Other adjustments to the user interface
  * Huge refactoring of the code
  * Lots of bug fixes

